<doc>
  <member name="D2D1_GAUSSIANBLUR_OPTIMIZATION">
    <summary>
      <para>The optimization mode for the <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/Direct2D/gaussian-blur">Gaussian blur effect</a>.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D2D1_GAUSSIANBLUR_OPTIMIZATION.D2D1_GAUSSIANBLUR_OPTIMIZATION_SPEED">
    <summary>
      <para>Applies internal optimizations such as pre-scaling at relatively small radii. Uses linear filtering.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D2D1_GAUSSIANBLUR_OPTIMIZATION.D2D1_GAUSSIANBLUR_OPTIMIZATION_BALANCED">
    <summary>
      <para>Uses the same optimization thresholds as Speed mode, but uses trilinear filtering.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D2D1_GAUSSIANBLUR_OPTIMIZATION.D2D1_GAUSSIANBLUR_OPTIMIZATION_QUALITY">
    <summary>
      <para>Only uses internal optimizations with large blur radii, where approximations are less likely to be visible. Uses trilinear filtering.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D2D1_GAUSSIANBLUR_OPTIMIZATION.D2D1_GAUSSIANBLUR_OPTIMIZATION_FORCE_DWORD">
    <summary></summary>
  </member>
</doc>